        "name": "Taser Barb",
        "slug": "taser-barb",
        "description": "<p>Effect: On hit, the target has this item's Taser Barbs embedded in them. The target can remove these Barbs with a Challenging Sleight of Hand or Intense Lift Check, or by moving further than 12m away from the item. The user can retract these Barbs as a Simple Action (either on a miss or while embedded in a creature).</p>",
